Directions:

Hot tea: Bring freshly drawn cold water to a rolling boil. Place 1 teabag for each desired

minutes. Pour into your cup; add milk and natural sweeteners to taste.

Iced Tea: (makes 1 qt/1L): Place 5 teabags into a teapot or heat resistant pitcher. Pour 1

with cold water. Garnish and sweeten to taste.
